    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a starter car? This vehicle is ready for someone with a little DIY spirit! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical attention and TLC, it's a great opportunity to get behind the wheel at a very accessible price point. Grab this diamond in the rough and give it the care it deserves!",
