    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection, the automobile exhibits reliable mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic presence. Benefiting from a consistent service history, this motorcar delivers a confident and sophisticated driving experience. We invite you to evaluate this exceptional balance of performance and value firsthand.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a dependable, great-looking car without the brand-new price tag. It runs super smoothly and is ready for its next adventure. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels on the road! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated power plant delivers linear throttle response through a precise G96 six-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recently refreshed suspension geometry including uprated bushings and Bilstein dampers. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal (RMS), mitigating common failure points of this architecture. Braking performance is sharp via four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the drivetrain provides a visceral, analog driving experience. A driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    }
